data.description:
Assumable 3.37% LOAN!! Welcome to your dream home in Harker Heights, TX! This stunning home is a true gem that offers the perfect blend of comfort and style. With 4 spacious bedrooms and 2 modern bathrooms, this home provides ample space for relaxation and privacy.

Step inside and be greeted by the inviting atmosphere that fills every corner of this house. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen, creating a warm and welcoming space for entertaining guests or simply enjoying quality time with loved ones. The air conditioner ensures that you stay cool and comfortable even during the hottest Texas summers.
